 die folgende 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma$
\end_inset

-Struktur:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathfrak{A}\oplus\mathfrak{B}\coloneqq\left(A\cup B,\left(R^{\mathfrak{A}}\cup R^{\mathfrak{B}}\right)_{R\in\sigma}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

